<div class="how_it_works_title">
  <b>How it works.</b>
</div>
<div class="how_it_works_right">
  <div class="how_it_works_image">
    <%= image_tag("HowItWorks1.png") %>
  </div>
  <div class="how_it_works_text" style="padding-left: 30px;">
    <div class="how_it_works_text_title">
      Post your delivery request.
    </div>
    <div class="how_it_works_text_content">
      Fill out basic details about your item.<br>
      You only have to tell us what you're sending, where from and to, and how much you will pay for the delivery.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="how_it_works_right">
  <div class="how_it_works_text" style=" padding-right: 30px;">
    <div class="how_it_works_text_title">
      Pick your transporter.
    </div>
    <div class="how_it_works_text_content">
      Choose the right person for your task.<br>
      Confirm one transporter out of the many who accept your delivery request.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="how_it_works_image">
    <%= image_tag("HowItWorks2.png") %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="how_it_works_right">
  <div class="how_it_works_image">
    <%= image_tag("HowItWorks3.png") %>
  </div>
  <div class="how_it_works_text" style="padding-left: 30px;">
    <div class="how_it_works_text_title">
      Authorize PayPal transaction.
    </div>
    <div class="how_it_works_text_content">
      Confirm delivery payment.<br>
      Transaction is processed only after transporter has successfully completed your delivery request.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="how_it_works_right">
  <div class="how_it_works_text" style=" padding-right: -10px;">
    <div class="how_it_works_text_title">
     Get your stuff delivered.
    </div>
    <div class="how_it_works_text_content">
      This is when your delivery happens.<br>
      Once it's complete, PayPal finishes the transaction.
      Rate the experience you've had with your transporter.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="how_it_works_image">
    <%= image_tag("HowItWorks4.png") %>
  </div>
</div>
<% if current_user.nil? %>
    <div class="signup_now" onclick="location.href='/signup'">
      <b>Get your own account!</b>
    </div>
<% end  %>